      <bioghist id="aspace_d053e3b3928c262926c3c1241affbb28">
         <head>Eugene Field, 1850-1895</head>
         <p>Eugene Field, Chicago poet and journalist.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_a52e4570ad145078057387734aa9efa5">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Contains autograph manuscript drafts of poems by Eugene Field and autograph letters signed from Field to various individuals.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_caedff4f502f257a948470795ae6b301">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Organized into two series: I. Correspondence, 1880-1898. II. Writings, 1888-1892.</p>  
      </arrangement>
